Author: Trevornon
Text: Ya I don’t have to worry about not having Coca Cola in Cuba, I’m addicted to the better version.

Author: paperklipp
Text: My SO and I went to Cuba in 2016 and they don’t sell Coke products there. We were both getting horrible migraines in the middle of every day and we couldn’t figure out what we were doing wrong: we were staying super hydrated, staying out of the sun, etc etc. On day three he was like “oh fuck, we’re going through caffeine withdrawal” because we both were drinking like two litres each of Diet Coke per day around that time.
